<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Pagamento</title>
<style>
body {
    background:#0f172a;
    color:white;
    font-family:Arial;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
}

.card {
    background:#1e293b;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:15px;
    width:350px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}

h2 { margin-bottom:10px; }

.plano {
    font-size:20px;
    margin:10px 0;
}

.valor {
    font-size:32px;
    color:#22c55e;
    margin:20px 0;
}

.pix-box {
    background:#0f172a;
    padding:12px;
    border-radius:8px;
    word-break: break-all;
    margin-bottom:10px;
    border:1px solid #333;
}

button {
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:8px;
    background:#22c55e;
    color:white;
    font-size:16px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

button:hover {
    background:#16a34a;
}

.info {
    margin-top:15px;
    font-size:14px;
    color:#ccc;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<h2>💰 Pagamento via PIX</h2>

<div class="plano">Plano: <%= plano.toUpperCase() %></div>

<div class="valor">R$ <%= valor %></div>

<div class="pix-box" id="pix">
49575071000101
</div>

<button onclick="copiar()">📋 Copiar Chave PIX</button>

<div class="info">
Após o pagamento, aguarde a liberação do sistema.<br>
Ou entre em contato para ativação imediata.
</div>

</div>

<script>
function copiar(){
    const text = document.getElementById("pix").innerText;
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
    alert("Chave PIX copiada!");
}
</script>

</body>
</html>